===Definitions===
{{zh-hanzi}}

# [[can]], [[may]], [[able to]]
#* {{zh-l|可能|possibly}}
#* {{zh-l|可以|can}}
#* {{zh-usex|這 袋子{zi} '''可''' 盛 五十 公斤。|This bag '''can''' hold 50 kilos.}}
#* {{zh-usex|他 沒有 家 '''可''' 住。|He had no place to live.}}
# (particle used for emphasis)
#* {{zh-usex|我 '''可''' 不 太 知道。|I don't '''really''' know.}}
# to [[approve]], to [[permit]]
#* {{zh-l|許可/许可|to permit, to allow}}
#* {{zh-l|認可/认可|to approve}}
# to [[suit]]
#* {{zh-l|可心|satisfying}}
# to be worth doing
#* {{zh-usex|展覽 的{dí}確 '''可''' 看。|The exhibition is really '''worth''' seeing.}}

===Usage notes===
* In compounds, {{zh-l|可}} can turn adjective and verbs into adjectives:
: {{zh-l|可吃|edible}}, {{zh-l|可愛/可爱|lovely}}, {{zh-l|可怜|pitiful}}

